03e甚至有点绝望。\u003cbr/\u003e但它，\u003cbr/\u003e是唯一一条，\u003cbr/\u003e能从逻辑上，\u003cbr/\u003e走得通的路。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"24kBWN2r\"\u003e如果你想知道，\u003cbr/\u003e我是如何运用这套逻辑，\u003cbr/\u003e一步步，\u003cbr/\u003e从井底爬出来，\u003cbr/\u003e并最终赚到第一桶金的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"sY90SkT7\"\u003e我把我的思考和实操过程，\u003cbr/\u003e都毫无保留地写在了这篇文章里，\u003cbr/\u003e有缘人可以看看：\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cb\u003e\u003cu\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kkE5NUU0FXqi-Z_S0QbgFA\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e阿凯：《 互联网创业之：第一桶金\u0026amp;0-1实操方法论》\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/u\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"590gWW86\"\u003e如果上面那个不方便，\u003cbr/\u003e也可以去我的公号【阿凯财富论】，\u003cbr/\u003e发送“第一桶金”这三个字，\u003cbr/\u003e系统会自动发给你。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"C-_Qle99\"\u003e希望它能成为，\u003cbr/\u003e你踩在脚下，\u003cbr/\u003e爬出井口的第一块，\u003cbr/\u003e坚实的“砖头”。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"__3jyUiv\"\u003e最后，\u003cbr/\u003e送你一句话，\u003cbr/\u003e是尼采说的：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-pid=\"mRCg4qf8\"\u003e那些杀不死你的，终将使你更强大。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"is_thanked":false,"is_nothelp":false,"voting":0},"is_labeled":false,"visited_count":349,"favorite_count":20,"answer_type":"normal","is_navigator":false,"navigator_vote":false,"vote_next_step":"vote"},"brief":"{\"source\": \"TS\", \"type\": \"answer\", \"id\": 1921239542041674958}","attached_info":"","action_card":false},{"id":"163_1750898571.650","type":"feed","offset":163,"verb":"TOPIC_ACKNOWLEDGED_ANSWER","created_time":1750898571,"updated_time":1750898571,"target":{"id":"1920980988894352853","type":"answer","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/answers/1920980988894352853","author":{"id":"8a3a7bda7c9ed0828805022bf060598f","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/people/8a3a7bda7c9ed0828805022bf060598f","user_type":"people","url_token":"leon-wone","name":"同富","headline":"要么共同富裕，要么犬儒主义","avatar_url":"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-5fbd6115d94680d384e8708ad17d0a98_l.jpg?source=b6762063","is_org":false,"g